<br>
To you guys I wish you well and if I am available I will still cast my mana rez any and all times for the good people of brell.  I am not anon so I get tons of tells but I like my job and most people that play clerics as there mains do also, my cleric has been with me for a long time and I still remember having bronze gear for along time before the world of twinks, which I have a lot of alts now.<br>
